{"id":9093,"content":"<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 28.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">今年以年，本刊发行部收到各地读者多次来电来函询问，《炎黄春秋》杂志</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2012</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年合订本什么时间开始邮购？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 28.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">经联系我社定点印制公司，他们表示，去年的合订本已经装订完成。本刊发行部表示，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">4</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月初《炎黄春秋》杂志</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2012</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年合订本就可以面向全国发行，现在可以汇款到炎黄春秋杂志社发行部邮购。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 28.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">部分读者反映，他们从某些网站上邮购到的“《炎黄春秋》杂志</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2012</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年合订本”存有质量问题。我社发行部表示，截止今年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月底，炎黄春秋杂志社发行部没有发行过</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2012</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年合订本。目前网上出售的“《炎黄春秋》杂志</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2012</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年合订本”属于某些网店私自装订出售的，与炎黄春秋杂志社发行部无关。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 28.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">在此，我们特别声明：《炎黄春秋》杂志各年度的合订本，惟一发行渠道为炎黄春秋杂志社发行部。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 28.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">《炎黄春秋》杂志</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2012</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年合订本为简装上下两册本，价格</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">120</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">元。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></STRONG></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 28.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">有关我社合订本的发行详情，请见本网站首页“订阅邮购”一栏：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 28.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">http://www.yhcqw.com/mall/zybdy/index.html<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>","title":"答读者：《炎黄春秋》杂志2012年合订本即将发行","time":1364404324999}